# Gaode (AMap) Web端 JS API — distinct from the backend GAODE_WEB_API_KEY
# (Web服务, server-side ONLY — MUST NEVER appear in frontend code).
# Get these from https://console.amap.com/dev/key/app → 创建「Web端(JS API)」应用.
# The JS API key is frontend-exposed (domain-restricted); the security code is
# a browser-side verification key (NOT a secret).
VITE_GAODE_JS_API_KEY=your_web_js_api_key
VITE_GAODE_JS_SECURITY_CODE=your_js_security_code

# NOTE: VITE_ prefix is REQUIRED — Vite only exposes env vars prefixed with
# VITE_ to import.meta.env.
#
# Pitfall 4 — Add localhost AND the production domain to the JS API key's
# 域名白名单 in the Gaode console (https://console.amap.com/dev/key/app →
# 我的应用 → 选中 JS API 应用 → 域名白名单) — else blank tiles.
#
# Pitfall 3 — The browser Geolocation API requires HTTPS in production
# (localhost is whitelisted automatically). For mobile/LAN testing use an
# HTTPS tunnel (ngrok, cloudflared).